@@TJvID3Controller.CopyFromID3v1
Summary
  Copies the ID3 v1 tag of the file to the relevant frames of the ID3 v2 tag.
Description
  Call CopyFromID3v1 to copy the ID3 v1 tag of the file specified by the FileName property to the
  ID3 v2 tag. The new tag isn't actually writtten to the file until you call Commit.

  The ID3 v2 frames that correspond to ID3 v1 fields are:

  <TABLE>
  ID3 v1        ID3 v2 frame ID                               Implemented by
  ------        ---------------                               --------------
  SongName      fiTitle                                       TJvID3TextFrame
  Artist        fiLeadArtist                                  TJvID3SimpleListFrame
  Album         fiAlbum                                       TJvID3TextFrame
  Year          fiRecordingTime (v2.4.0) or fiYear (v2.3.0)   TJvID3TimestampFrame, TJvID3NumberFrame resp.
  Comment       fiComment                                     TJvID3ContentFrame
  Genre         fiContentType                                 TJvID3TextFrame
  </TABLE>
  The tag controller must be active - Do this by setting Active to true or calling Open.
Parameters
  DoOverwrite - Specifies whether to overwrite the values of existing frames by the values of the
                 ID3 v1 tag.
Return value
  Returns true on success, false on failure.
See Also
  <LINK CopyFromID3v1Ctrl>, <LINK CopyToID3v1>, <LINK CopyToID3v1Ctrl>

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvID3Controller.CopyFromID3v1Ctrl
Summary
  Copies the properties of the ID3 v1 component to the relevant frames of the ID3 v2 tag.
