----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvID3Controller.WriteVersionAs
Summary
  Enforces the tag to be written as a specific version.
Description
  Use WriteVersionAs to enforce the tag to be written as a specific version.

  You can either specify:

  * that you don't care with what version the tag will be written: the tag will be written   with the
