@@TJvID3DoubleListFrame
Summary
  Represents a frame containing the names of those involved, and how they were involved with the
  audio.
Description
  The following <LINK TJvID3FrameID,frame identifiers> are supported by TJvID3DoubleListFrame.

  <TABLE>
  Frame ID, name              Description
  -----------------           -----------
  fiInvolvedPeople -          The 'Involved people list' frame contains the names of those involved, and
   <C>IPLS</C>                 how they were involved. <b>(Not in v2.4.0 tags)</b>
  fiMusicianCreditList -      The 'Musician credits list' frame is intended as a mapping between
   <C>TMCL</C>                 instruments and the musician that played it. <b>(Only in v2.4.0 tags)</b>
  fiInvolvedPeople2 -         The 'Involved people list' is very similar to the musician credits
   <C>TIPL</C>                 list, but maps between functions, like producer, and names. <b>(Only in v2.4.0 tags)</b>
  </TABLE>

  The fiInvolvedPeople frame is deprecated as of version 2.4 and replaced by fiMusicianCreditList and
  fiInvolvedPeople2. These last two are only valid in version 2.4.

  There may only be one fiInvolvedPeople frame in a version 2.2 or version 2.3 tag, and there may
  only be one fiMusicianCreditList and one fiInvolvedPeople2 frame in a version 2.4 tag.
