@@TJvID3UserFrame.FindOrCreate
Summary
  Returns a TJvID3UserFrame frame with a specific index.
Description
  Call FindOrCreate to search in an ID3 tag for a user defined text information frame with a specific
  index.
  If there is no such frame then one is created. The tag controller specified by AController must be
  active - Do this by setting <LINK TJvID3Controller.Active,Active> to true or calling <LINK
  TJvID3Controller.Open,Open>.
Parameters
  AController - Specifies the tag controller that holds an ID3 v2 tag where in to search.
  Index       - Specifies the index of the user defined text frame. Specifying 0 for Index searches
               for the first user text link frame in the tag, specifying 1 for the second, etc.
Return value
  Returns a TJvID3UserFrame frame with the specified owner identifier, that was found in the ID3 tag,
  or - when no such frame was found - a newly created frame.
